            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>毅嘉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2402:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2402\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2402-TW</a>)16日09:02股價下跌5.2元，報67.2元，跌幅7.18%，成交6,829張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>毅嘉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2402:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2402\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2402-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為各種電子塑膠、矽膠字鍵、鍵盤及其組裝。軟性電路版及其組裝。智慧財產權業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲27.24%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.64%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+31,032 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+24,537 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+6,495 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,008 張</li> <li>融券增減：-114 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
